ltl2rabin.LTL

Interface IVisitable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the accept function (and also the return type of the visit function of the IVisitor).
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    And, Boolean, F, Formula, G, Or, U, Variable, X

    public interface IVisitable<T>
    Interface for LTL formulas. A formula that implements this interface can accept an IVisitor.
